  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1208760/extras/4a32236e6e213571139ec5c21a2b83e1.avif?t=1760026619\" width=618 height=194 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1208760/extras/f399ffc8ff793b525e0c7fabf9a150ab.webp?t=1760026619\" width=618 height=19 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>View From Below</strong> is a story-driven, turn-based RPG. You play as a struggling student called <i>ASH</i> who is captured by a mysterious presence, and taken to a scary new world. You'll fight demons, solve puzzles, and unravel several horrifying mysteries, on your quest to escape it.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Escape a nightmare world, to save your own.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1208760/extras/6e25a5e540a9c86f4f4478efd8d273a7.webp?t=1760026619\" width=618 height=19 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Fight <strong>exciting battles</strong> with a fun twist: lean left and right to <i>EVADE</i> enemy attacks!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Defeat huge, <strong>epic bosses</strong>!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Solve dozens of <strong>puzzles and minigames</strong>!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Explore a strange world seeped in <strong>mystery, secrets, and hidden lore</strong>!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Experience a <strong>heartfelt story</strong> with <strong>multiple endings</strong>! (Including a hidden \"true\" ending.)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Unlock a <strong>New Game+ mode</strong> with harder fights, and new reveals...</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Created almost entirely by one moron (me!)</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >View From Below is a little bit dark, a little bit funny, and has quite a lot to say. It's inspired by games like Earthbound and Undertale, and movies like Donnie Darko and Alice in Wonderland.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game means a lot to me. I hope it'll mean a lot to you, too.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1208760/extras/6b3d25e7bf7bef184714e7b40afba251.webp?t=1760026619\" width=618 height=19 /></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >LFOB </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Matthew Pablo </p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1208760/extras/4a32236e6e213571139ec5c21a2b83e1.avif?t=1760026619\" width=618 height=194 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1208760/extras/f399ffc8ff793b525e0c7fabf9a150ab.webp?t=1760026619\" width=618 height=19 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>View From Below</strong> is a story-driven, turn-based RPG. You play as a struggling student called <i>ASH</i> who is captured by a mysterious presence, and taken to a scary new world. You'll fight demons, solve puzzles, and unravel several horrifying mysteries, on your quest to escape it.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Escape a nightmare world, to save your own.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1208760/extras/6e25a5e540a9c86f4f4478efd8d273a7.webp?t=1760026619\" width=618 height=19 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Fight <strong>exciting battles</strong> with a fun twist: lean left and right to <i>EVADE</i> enemy attacks!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Defeat huge, <strong>epic bosses</strong>!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Solve dozens of <strong>puzzles and minigames</strong>!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Explore a strange world seeped in <strong>mystery, secrets, and hidden lore</strong>!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Experience a <strong>heartfelt story</strong> with <strong>multiple endings</strong>! (Including a hidden \"true\" ending.)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Unlock a <strong>New Game+ mode</strong> with harder fights, and new reveals...</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Created almost entirely by one moron (me!)</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >View From Below is a little bit dark, a little bit funny, and has quite a lot to say. It's inspired by games like Earthbound and Undertale, and movies like Donnie Darko and Alice in Wonderland.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game means a lot to me. I hope it'll mean a lot to you, too.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1208760/extras/6b3d25e7bf7bef184714e7b40afba251.webp?t=1760026619\" width=618 height=19 /></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >LFOB </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Matthew Pablo </p>",
